headline: HP: Q1 Earnings Preview, Sentiment Low With AI PCs A Potential Catalyst For Growth In 2025
summary: HP is positioned for a potential rebound in 2025 due to Windows 10's end-of-life and the rise of AI PCs. See why I rate HPQ stock a buy.
